{"tid":121170,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"當183cm愛上150cm 「錫得耐會頸痛」","createTime":"2017-02-15T04:27:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T04:19:38.000Z","uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f191bbf80f951351c1ca37f0ff2b78a5b2c2601e","tid":121170,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T04:27:49.000Z","msg":"【最萌身高差】當183cm愛上150cm 「錫得耐會頸痛」<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/supplement/20170214/56299445\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsupplement%2F20170214%2F56299445&d=o1jNmZJj5m3DpFdm5BDgvwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=fd581ebd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsupplement%2F20170214%2F56299445&h=1389d09b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/supplement/20170214/56299445</a><br />\n<br />\n有人說15cm是最佳接吻身高，亦有人說20cm最適合壁咚，日本甚至稱30cm以上身高差為「最萌身高差」，是最佳的戀愛高度。這對拍了兩年半拖的情，身高150cm的區家恩（Nicole）和183cm的何允恆（Phoenix），擁有33cm的距離。就等他們話你知身高差生活會面對甚麼麻煩，又會否因為身高差影響感情？即刻去片！<br />\n<a href=\"http://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/02/14/3277122/20170215_Vvvsub720_clean_w.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvideo.appledaily.com.hk%2Fmcp%2Fencode%2F2017%2F02%2F14%2F3277122%2F20170215_Vvvsub720_clean_w.mp4&d=o1jNmZJj5m3DpFdm5BDgvwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=1dcfbcca\" target=\"_blank\">http://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/02/14/3277122/20170215_Vvvsub720_clean_w.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170213/large/1486981007_b96b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170213%2Flarge%2F1486981007_b96b.jpg&h=cc2546dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n150cm的區家恩（Nicole）和183cm的何允恆（Phoenix），相差33cm。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170213/large/1486981008_514b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170213%2Flarge%2F1486981008_514b.jpg&h=87f1333d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n家裏只能用連身鏡，方便二人身高也能照到。（受訪者提供）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170213/large/1486981010_3a57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170213%2Flarge%2F1486981010_3a57.jpg&h=1be1a4cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n情侶愛自拍是常識吧，但每次Nicole自拍均告失敗收場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170213/large/1486981011_54f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170213%2Flarge%2F1486981011_54f5.jpg&h=780580c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNicole接觸不到上方的地鐵扶手，每次都要靠Phoenix一對人肉扶手。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170213/large/1486981012_5567.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170213%2Flarge%2F1486981012_5567.jpg&h=1a7ac133&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNicole對於接吻都有意見：「錫得久會頸痛！」"},{"pid":"17c1c9be4c5085d80a0cb3ff771b6743f23ef842","tid":121170,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T04:29:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新聞？"},{"pid":"b0215cafd1b07a0009df47628af42a76bc1f3d3c","tid":121170,"uid":23162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T04:36:32.000Z","msg":"第時你屌閪仲大鑊呀，一路扑條女一路聞你隔肋底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌到一半佢暈咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb813e1e7441ff5aad0534801286f93c6c81818","tid":121170,"uid":29040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T05:05:29.000Z","msg":"關我撚事咩 咁都新聞"},{"pid":"28c2272567bcc7c5d2b8893b7c1662ea0c4056a9","tid":121170,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB